Direct Known Subclasses:
DebugPDBAtom, NNPDBAtom
public class PDBAtom
extends Atom
implements java.lang.Cloneable, IPDBAtom

Represents the idea of an atom as used in PDB files. It contains extra fields normally associated with atoms in such files.

See Also:
Atom, Serialized Form
